{
  "stem": "2435.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on-- that was much later on-- when we went out very little only, she was able to get extra food for us, while we had a special food card where there was a J on it where you were limited to buy food.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were limited to buy eggs, and bread, and milk because we were Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to show this card to the grocery store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nana, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that is good that you ask me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, she-- at night, she went down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She knew there was a store called [NON-ENGLISH], which was a general food store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went down there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She knew quite a lot of people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She got extra eggs, and milk, and bread for us, and came up the back way, back stairs way up during the night.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was about 11 or 12 o'clock she came up with that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, it was-- there was a great danger involved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the way, she had to leave in '30-- after Kristallnacht, she had to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was not allowed, as a Christian person, to work with Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she stayed in a little apartment, a room nearby, so that she would be able to smuggle up food for us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was absolutely wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Marta ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fromholz ?] was her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was-- she came to us when my brother was born on the 28th of November 1914.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she stayed with us, actually, until the last day that we immigrated in the way of-- she came with us on the day that we immigrated to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a station where all the Jews had to meet.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
